  EffectDiscription_ENG: "[When Attacking] You may play 1 [Diaboromon] Token without
    paying its memory cost. (Diaboromon Tokens are level 6 white Digimon with a memory
    cost of 14\uFF0C 3000 DP\uFF0C and are Mega form\uFF0C Unidentified type\uFF0C
    and Unknown attribute.)[All Turns] When this Digimon would be deleted in battle\uFF0C
    you may delete one of your other [Diaboromon] to prevent this Digimon from being
    deleted. "
